      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified+1\n\nPassed enforced test review-ldiskfs-dne on CentOS 7.0/x86_64 uploaded by Onyx Autotest from onyx-61vm1: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/5c252fd0-b191-4ed3-a666-2fe22791ec3c ran 4 tests.",
